The mission of a word bold">archon</span> is to protect such noble concepts as "virtue," "goodness," and "charity." Using the power of truenames, they travel far from Mount Celestia to make sure such words inspire the good-hearted everywhere -- and evildoers that face the wrath of a word archon's voice raised against them. 

